node.text: MSU is a place full of possibilities, promise and people determined to make a difference. You are part of something bigger here. And when you leave, you will be ready to change the world. Because you are a Spartan, and Spartans Will.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Michigan State University on September 01, 2021. May be an image of 3 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text: Whether it's your first day or your last first day, have the BEST day, Spartans. 📷: @safakaraein

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Michigan State University on August 31, 2021. May be an image of sky, road, twilight and brick wall.

node.text: A new year begins tomorrow. You may be feeling excited, nervous or even scared. Whatever you’re feeling, just know you are not alone. We’re in this together. Here's to a great year, Spartans.

node.text: There are so many special places on MSU’s campus waiting for you.

node.accessibility_caption: A baby dressed in MSU clothing sits on the base of the Spartan statue with her father’s arm around her, smiling, also wearing MSU clothing.

node.text: Sophie, a future Spartan, visited campus for the first time. 💚 📷: @1motor29

node.accessibility_caption: A student holding his hands up over the stadium Spartan helmet logo, forming a heart shape, with trees lining both sides of the photo and blue skies in the background

node.text: The moment you step onto campus, MSU becomes part of you. You’re a Spartan — now and forever.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Michigan State University on August 20, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Home is where the helmet is. Go Green forever.

node.accessibility_caption: Cowles house on a summer evening.

node.text: East Lansing is looking better than ever, and we can’t wait for you to be here, experience everything new and feel at home at your favorites. 💚
